      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through its six individual throttle bodies and optimized by high-pressure double VANOS. Power is managed via a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and delivered to the rear wheels through a variable M-differential lock. The chassis remains composed with a reinforced rear subframe and updated bushings, ensuring the MacPherson front and multi-link rear suspension geometry stays true under load. Recent valve clearance adjustments and a cooling system refresh make this a robust, driver-focused example.",
