    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This unit maintains excellent compression across all cylinders, with the Double VANOS system functioning within factory tolerances and a recent valve adjustment performed via shim-and-bucket. The drivetrain consists of a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox linked to a 3.62 limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal torque distribution. The chassis remains rigid, having undergone a preventative subframe reinforcement procedure. Suspension is composed of refreshed control arm bushings and MacPherson struts up front with a multi-link rear setup, providing precise turn-in and lateral stability. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the mechanical synchronization and throttle response from the individual throttle bodies remain sharp and visceral.",
